          "sent_mt": "2026-06-01T06:09:56-06:00",
          "text": "The mixer auger is not functioning properly. The internal agitator is not rotating even though the motor is running. The lead opened the machine and found that a connecting piece between the motor and the agitator appears to be missing. We are searching for the part, and maintenance has been notified.",
